column1: # Each row: [timestamp, seq, dt_s, theta, roll, pitch, vel_x, vel_y, v_forward, gyro_z, accel_x, accel_y, accel_z] -- all values are directly from Sphero sensors. Conversions: accel raw in g, *9.81 for m/s^2; gyro raw in deg/s, *pi/180 for rad/s; velocity raw in mm/s, /1000 for m/s; v_forward is projection onto heading (see code).
